{
  "stem": "11179.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have to take my hat off of all the actors and actresses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's really amazing what they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They came to camps, just a couple of people-- maybe two or three-- and made us laugh.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as they said later on, that was their pay.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They put up lavish performances.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went up-- up to, like, operettas or operas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw the opera [? common ?] in Shanghai there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't-- I really couldn't afford to see many. 'Merry Widower' I saw seven times because we ushering and helping out, and my boss was helping out with lighting and everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used movie theaters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the-- in the restricted area, there were only two theaters in the restricted area we could use.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But even on-- in-- in the little community rooms we had-- like in the camp, there was the room [INAUDIBLE] people playing cards and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had a little stage set up [INAUDIBLE] plays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I saw-- I saw many plays, mostly were done in German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because the-- the audience was German and-- and-- and the actors were German or Austrian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were-- a lot of them were not professional actors and some of them were professional actors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One man I've seen before many times in Berlin in the Jewish theater, for instance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Fritz [INAUDIBLE] was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was also a cartoonist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was also a very good actor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I've seen 'Gypsy Baron,' 'Countess Maritza.' I don't know if they mean anything to you, and 'The Merry Widower.' I saw 'Carmen.' I-- I-- I saw more than that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had a regular theater that several theater groups, actually several.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
